<plot>A delightful story of a small boy who visits a retirement home and makes friends with "Miss Nancy" and helps her improve her memory so she can continue teach him to play the organ. But first, he has to discover what memory is. In the meanwhile Wilfrid's family are not very sensitive to the need of Wilfrid to visit the retirement home until they have an opportunity to observe Wilfrid and Miss Nancy together at the organ and discover the importance of the interactions between children and elder adults.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?657263</url></doc>
